.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
Game: poker, backgammon
Nationality: dutch, egyptian
Pet: cat, horse
Sport: climbing, soccer
1. Sport:soccer is in an even position##4
2. Nationality:egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. Game:backgammon == Nationality:dutch##1
4. Pet:cat is on the left of Nationality:egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Game           | backgammon | poker    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| Pet           | cat         | horse    |
| Sport         | climbing    | soccer   |

